{"tid":426301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"魯比奧：《香港人權與民主法案》強化對港政策　聯署提名雙學傘運競逐諾獎","createTime":"2017-10-06T13:25:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T03:23:19.000Z","uid":13468,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4be67137285bcad34c391c11f3bfcd8c5664aa73","tid":426301,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T13:25:37.000Z","msg":"魯比奧：《香港人權與民主法案》強化對港政策　正收集聯署提名雙學傘運競逐諾獎<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.post852.com/231131/%E9%AD%AF%E6%AF%94%E5%A5%A7%EF%BC%9A%E3%80%8A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E8%88%87%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88%E3%80%8B%E5%BC%B7%E5%8C%96%E5%B0%8D%E6%B8%AF%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E3%80%80/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F231131%2F%25E9%25AD%25AF%25E6%25AF%2594%25E5%25A5%25A7%25EF%25BC%259A%25E3%2580%258A%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25A1%2588%25E3%2580%258B%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%258C%2596%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2594%25BF%25E7%25AD%2596%25E3%2580%2580%2F&d=wHzxtsvRFk5DG64ZpVbQqwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=a8d8937b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.post852.com/231131/%E9%AD%AF%E6%AF%94%E5%A5%A7%EF%BC%9A%E3%80%8A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E8%88%87%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88%E3%80%8B%E5%BC%B7%E5%8C%96%E5%B0%8D%E6%B8%AF%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E3%80%80/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/06103420/fgnh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2F06103420%2Ffgnh.jpg&h=10148e95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國國會及行政當局中國委員會（CECC）昨日向美國國會提交本年度的報告書，委員會主席、共和黨參議員魯比奧（Marco Rubio）向記者表示，國會正審議的《香港人權與民主法案》（Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Bill），目的是強化目前美國對港的政策，又稱將發動參眾兩院的議員進行聯署，提名現正被囚的「雙學三子」香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒、主席羅冠聰與學聯前秘書長周永康，以及整個「雨傘運動」競逐明年的諾貝爾和平獎。<br />\n<br />\n魯比奧認為，大家需要重新思考香港主權移交時中國所作出的承諾，而有關承諾正不斷被破壞，目前新法案未見有明顯的反對意見，相信將於國會獲得通過，並為香港帶來影響。<br />\n<br />\n現時美國國會對港政策主要依據在1992年通過的《美國－香港政策法》（United States-Hong Kong Policy Act），將香港視為與內地有別的「非主權政治實體」，特別在進出口管制、商貿合作等領域。法案亦要求國務院每年度對香港自治狀況進行評估，以及向國會提交報告。<br />\n<br />\n（圖片來源：Marco Rubio fb）"},{"pid":"86c2157cba2b794d4bab11a84aca557526511d0e","tid":426301,"uid":13468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T13:27:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/ws/624/amz/worldservice/live/assets/images/2016/11/17/161117043223_facebook_joshua_wong_20161117_0123g_976x865.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef-1.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fws%2F624%2Famz%2Fworldservice%2Flive%2Fassets%2Fimages%2F2016%2F11%2F17%2F161117043223_facebook_joshua_wong_20161117_0123g_976x865.jpg&h=0af6d675&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b902c2dd645677e55dd194c9ec9c1f4242071653","tid":426301,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T13:35:11.000Z","msg":"嚟料喇"},{"pid":"3d55589bb0f70a792b952509afc2e63d06edf842","tid":426301,"uid":13468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T13:38:32.000Z","msg":"之鋒即將成為偉人"},{"pid":"b76becf314c1bb3fefaa5b86ab4744b1a7942f07","tid":426301,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T13:42:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c09b05e8393782849fc1467aeb0efcbbfd0267ad","tid":426301,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T03:39:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75dd63d909099a1c78133269f01321358a514b08","tid":426301,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T03:40:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"050de6f6f6337f113d134bc800c58794f6c37639","tid":426301,"uid":1254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T03:55:19.000Z","msg":"無人推？"},{"pid":"175ad840a55b39b94530a699cb52dcb2da7cc6f8","tid":426301,"uid":138689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T04:24:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"959fc64976940935ef0214cc2216fb77f9b07c20","tid":426301,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T09:39:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"154fe20d1516843612e828c46771aa94844cecf7","tid":426301,"uid":69794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T09:47:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e85293c3980b191382cb368eef12bf47a4ff7330","tid":426301,"uid":26506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T09:50:58.000Z","msg":"除咗加拿大同墨西哥, US-HK Policy Act算唔算一個國會議員最易入手嘅外交/國際議題?"},{"pid":"8f9cc4b5336e81ea54c443c6b9712760e653c687","tid":426301,"uid":69794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T12:01:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除咗加拿大同墨西哥, US-HK Policy Act算唔算一個國會議員最易入手嘅外交/國際議題?</blockquote><br />\n做緊poli/IR project?"},{"pid":"3b56ae0819408d6389d8f73a4c9849d14a97710b","tid":426301,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T12:39:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>除咗加拿大同墨西哥, US-HK Policy Act算唔算一個國會議員最易入手嘅外交/國際議題?</blockquote><br />\n做緊poli/IR project?</blockquote><br />\n吓鳩噏鳩問咋喎, 做乜咁諗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3453c2c1502531590c22a2003701919885f4677","tid":426301,"uid":69794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:01:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>除咗加拿大同墨西哥, US-HK Policy Act算唔算一個國會議員最易入手嘅外交/國際議題?</blockquote><br />\n做緊poli/IR project?</blockquote><br />\n吓鳩噏鳩問咋喎, 做乜咁諗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢排已經有人開始做project,所以好奇問下"},{"pid":"d91fc5d3e040d52021334b78094e18f8e42188a2","tid":426301,"uid":132896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:11:37.000Z","msg":"其實呢啲獎既幕後裁判都幾左膠<br />\n或者幾反暴力（雖則絕對唔鼓勵暴力武力，但佢地總會有合理既一面；或者班友可以諗下自己國家以前啲歷史，反思下唔用武力自己個國家會係點樣）<br />\n當然如果頒獎提名涉及一啲強硬派右派，又會擔心變相鼓勵以暴易暴既方法<br />\n<br />\n虛偽啲講<br />\n和平非暴力<br />\n同武力反抗<br />\n兩邊不可少"},{"pid":"0402e38d013c38c925ad70a3e6a98e6bc525f271","tid":426301,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:31:22.000Z","msg":"Introduced in Senate (11/16/2016)<br />\n<br />\n搞左成年, 依家點?"},{"pid":"6ef097f46f1740f8045ba4afe1dad17bbf9e86ca","tid":426301,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:32:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之鋒即將成為偉人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n司徒華二世"},{"pid":"3e42acac85ba557f19a6782a797e5cbf06b6d305","tid":426301,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T03:23:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}